<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tell Me More - Gaming Hub</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #010E1F;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .section-heading {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #4caf50;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .section-content {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .back-button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            display: block;
            margin: 30px auto;
            text-align: center;
            width: 200px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="section-heading">Welcome to Gaming Hub</h1>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Gaming Hub is your ultimate destination for online gaming fun! We offer a wide range of exciting games to suit every taste and skill level.</p>
            <p>Whether you're a casual gamer looking to unwind after a long day or a competitive player seeking thrilling challenges, Gaming Hub has something for you.</p>
            <p>Our platform features daily games, weekly tournaments, and interactive community events to keep you entertained and engaged.</p>
            <p>Join our vibrant gaming community today and discover the excitement of Gaming Hub!</p>
            <p>Don't miss out on the latest updates and special offers. Subscribe to our newsletter and follow us on social media!</p>
        </div>

        <a href="/" class="back-button">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
